516
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:45,180
Ruofeng.

517
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:49,080
How come you have the same name as Xiao Ruofeng?

518
00:40:49,080 --> 00:40:51,660
Now you've got me stumped.

519
00:40:53,720 --> 00:40:57,820
Although he and I are both named Ruofeng, he's wind that will become a dragon.

520
00:40:57,820 --> 00:41:01,520
People want to use him to ascend to the Ninth Heaven and transform into a dragon.

521
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:03,420
Whereas I'm a shadowless wind.

522
00:41:03,420 --> 00:41:07,660
I cannot be traced, cannot be found, and yet I'm everywhere.

523
00:41:07,660 --> 00:41:09,780
We are not the same.

524
00:41:21,020 --> 00:41:22,400
What kind of lightness technique is that?

525
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:24,700
Cloud-Stepping Wind.

526
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:31,080
I'm looking forward to your performance on the exam.

527
00:41:31,080 --> 00:41:34,380
Just make sure you don't die.

528
00:41:39,560 --> 00:41:42,560
