529
00:41:42,560 --> 00:41:46,820
You've underestimated Tianqi City as well as the Academy's exam.

530
00:41:54,860 --> 00:41:57,640
Did I underestimate Tianqi City?

531
00:41:59,740 --> 00:42:02,240
I never underestimate anything.

532
00:42:02,240 --> 00:42:08,800
I just believe that with a sword in my hand, I'll be the one who will make it to the end.

533
00:42:18,040 --> 00:42:23,820
